data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of the charming Sanders Beach Community. Located just moments away from the vibrant downtown scene, the serene waterfront and amazing venues like the Pensacola Yacht Club and the Sanders Beach Community Center. This meticulously crafted 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless elegance. As you step into the inviting foyer, you're greeted by an abundance of natural light that highlights the open floor plan and gleaming laminate wood floors throughout the first floor. The spacious living area seamlessly connects to the dining room, providing an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The well-appointed kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space, catering to both culinary enthusiasts and everyday convenience. A breakfast nook overlooks the backyard, creating a cozy spot for morning coffee or casual meals. Retreat upstairs to the master suite, a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring a generous layout, 2 large walk-in closets, and an en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a water closet. The 2 additional bedrooms are oversized and therefore, provide more than comfortable accommodations for family or guests, while the shared full bath ensures convenience for all. Unlike many homes downtown this one has a private backyard, perfect for al fresco dinners. The proximity to downtown ensures you're just moments away from eclectic shops, fine dining, and cultural attractions. Meanwhile, the nearby waterfront beckons with its scenic views and recreational opportunities. Don't miss the chance to make this residence your own and experience the best of urban living in a tranquil setting. The city of Pensacola is planning to purchase the building across the streeet and tear it down.  This will create a full waterview from this home.  A water retention pond will be builit which may eliminate need for flood ins.
